        "content": "# Live ROI Tracking from /evaluate, /evaluate/bulk, /evaluate/bulk/stream, /intake/evaluate\n\n**Top row** = ROI accrued in the **selected time range** (responds to the time picker).  \n**Bottom row** = **lifetime cumulative** totals since first ever rule processed.  \n\nDeduplication by `request_id:item_index` prevents double-counting. Bootstrap from `decision_history.jsonl` survives restarts. Refresh: 5s."
